name: Aaron N. Martin
birth_place: 美国,田纳西州,纳什维尔

last_movies.title: 希拉里的美国：民主党秘史

introduction: Aaron N Martin was born on March 25, 1975 in Nashville, Tennessee. He is an actor known for his work in "The Great Hanging" and "Fairview Chronicles" by Jonathan Paul and The Last Whistle by Rob Smat. Aaron first got involved with acting at the Denton Community Theatre and Musical Theatre of Denton, while living in the North Texas area. He now resides back in his hometown of East Nashville, Tennessee
